"{\"uid\": \"techmoran.com-2024-08-06-google-doodle-today-celebrates-artistic-swimming-at-the-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"TheParis Olympic Gamesare in full swing, and today is the second day of artistic swimming.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 90, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This sport, also known as synchronized swimming, combines elements of swimming, gymnastics, and dance.\", \"from\": 91, \"to\": 193, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is both beautiful and graceful, requiring athletes to have strength, flexibility, and coordination.\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 296, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Today'sGoogle Doodlecelebrates the second day of artistic swimming at the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 384, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Doodle features three swimmers performing a synchronized routine in a pool.\", \"from\": 385, \"to\": 464, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They are dressed in colorful costumes and surrounded by bubbles, set against a light blue background with the Google logo in the bottom right corner.\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 575, \"end\": 586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_logo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google logo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_logo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_logo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Google Doodle marks the second day of artistic swimming at the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 691, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Artistic swimming is a relatively new addition to the Olympic Games, having been introduced in 1984.\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Since then, it has rapidly gained popularity and is now practiced in over 100 countries.\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 881, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Initially, the sport included only solo and duet categories for women.\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 955, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2017, the sport experienced a major rebranding when its international governing body renamed it from \\\"synchronized swimming\\\" to \\\"artistic swimming.\\\"\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 1108, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This change was intended to eliminate confusion about the sport's nature, emphasizing its artistic aspects rather than just synchronization.\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1250, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Artistic swimming is a challenging yet highly rewarding sport.\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1314, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It requires dedication and practice but is also very enjoyable.\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1378, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are looking for a new sport to try or want to get in shape, artistic swimming is an excellent choice.\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1487, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Log in to leave a comment  TechMoran is Africa's top media for tech entrepreneurs and investors and does an insightful coverage of Africa's technology and startup scene through its digital platforms and monthly #TechNights and its annual TechMoran Startup Festival & Awards dubbed #StartupEast, the biggest startup event in East Africa.\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1825, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1813, \"end\": 1824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9803449984132946, \"rank\": 0.018546684809110793, \"text\": \"East Africa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Contact us at info@techmoran.com  \\u00a9 TechMoran.\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1873, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1894, \"entities\": []}]}"